data.description: Perfect starter home in Del City! HUGE family room greets you with built-in shelves and a wood burning fireplace. Closets and storage space abounds in the main part of the home. Kitchen is a great size, and includes eat-in dining area. Don't miss the utility space just off the kitchen/dining area. Three bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms round out the floor plan. Out back you'll find an entertainer's dream! Pool has railing and ladders for ease of access. Cabana provides a great place to hang! Brand new 10 ft' fencing gives the ultimate level of privacy in the backyard. All situated on a corner lot in a cul-de-sac, located right off I-40 & Sooner Rd for an easy commute! Property to be sold as-is.
